     4→* COMP 421/521 Lab 3 (Yalnix yfs) test code          *
     5→*    read_write_seek_stat.c                          *
     6→*                                                    *
     7→* Author                                             *
     8→*  Bumjin Im (imbumjin@rice.edu)                     *
